<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.7">
<l>kuṭaṅka ḷeṭuttēṟa viṭṭuk kūttāṭa vallaveṅ kōvē</l>
<l>maṭaṅkoḷ matimukat tārai mālceyya vallaveṉ maintā</l>
<l>viṭantiṭ ṭiraṇiyaṉ neñcai yirupiḷa vākamuṉ kīṇṭāy</l>
<l>kuṭantaik kiṭantaveṅ kōvē kurukkattip pūccūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our King, able to dance a dance upon pots raised high!</l>
<l>My son, able to trick the moon-faced ladies!</l>
<l>You who long ago cleaved in two pieces and dug out Hiranya’s heart,</l>
<l>Our king who sleeps in Kuṭantai,</l>
<l>come so that [I can] adorn [you] with Kurukkatti blossoms!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
